          "order": 3,
          "title": "REACT APPS",
          "summary": "Even the best frontend devs can forget accessibility checks from time to time - that’s why catching them with tests and lint rules are helpful. This blog covers how you can write accessibility tests in most of the popular testing and linting frameworks and how to integrate these tests into an application’s CI/CD.",
